title: #92Noon! Zimm/Podolsky/Leber/Jonny/Birk/Adelman
description: Some Wolves POBO news and "Solving the Seahawks" to begin, followed by a Zimmer/PA Xs & Os chat, then author Rich Podolsky to finish the first hour....Leber in studio, and Jonny Athletic get us to the final stretch that includes the Birk Bit, former Wolves/current Nuggets asst coach David Adelman, and the Action Segment to close!
